Coverages to Keep Your Business Moving
Protecting the spectrum of commercial autos.




Commercial Auto Insurance


      Our breadth of underwriting experience means we don't have to restrict ourselves to one aspect of the 
      commercial auto insurance market. Instead, National Indemnity Company insures a wide range of vehicles 
      for a wide range of businesses -- even those with unique coverage needs.
    



      To protect your company from the unexpected, turn to the company with an A++ rating by A.M. Best* and 
      more than half a century of experience insuring commercial vehicles.
    
*As of May 21, 2014.  For the latest rating, access www.ambest.com.


Commercial Auto Products



Business Auto

Auto insurance coverage for large or small businesses.


         


Learn More





Commercial Trucks and Truckers

Insurance coverage for a wide-range of trucks operating locally or across the country, including commercial pickup trucks, tow trucks, dump trucks, and tractor-trailers.


         


Learn More





Passenger Transport

Insurance coverage for vehicles that transport people — from charter buses to day care vans.


         


Learn More




Specialty Operations

Insurance coverage for many other types of vehicle operations, the scope of which may surprise you.


         


Learn More




 
 


