﻿




National Liability &  Fire Insurance Company



















Partner with a Secure Source for Property & Casualty Insurance


			            National Liability & Fire Insurance Company is a wholly owned 
						subsidiary of Berkshire Hathaway Inc. As a result, policyholders can 
						feel very confident about the financial strength of the company 
						providing their coverage. 
			            Over a half century old, NL&F has been writing automobile coverage 
						since day one and remains active in that area today. More recently, 
						we have developed a growing interest in providing Workers’ 
						Compensation coverage and now have the ability to write business in 
						most parts of the country. Above and beyond those specialties, we 
						consider other industry opportunities. 

			            Creating a positive customer experience is always an important part 
						of our focus. We view insurance as a partnership and work closely 
						with our policyholders to provide professional service throughout 
						the term of a policy. 







 




 





 




 




















