National Liability & Fire Insurance Company










































About Us

    A member of the Berkshire Hathaway family, National Liability & Fire is a wholly owned subsidiary of the Berkshire
    Hathaway Group. Over a half century old, NL&F is rated A++ (Superior) by A.M. Best Company - one of the premier
    sources of independent analysis about the financial strength and overall operations of insurers worldwide. As a
    result, policyholders can feel very confident about the financial strength of the company providing their coverage.

As a Workers' Compensation Specialist . . .

	NL&F is equipped to provide expert services in all disciplines - from initial billing through claims.

Contact Information

	NL&F Processing
	P.O. Box 113247
	Stamford, CT 06911-3247

	
	For Claims:
	Toll Free 844-549-2512
	Claims FAX 203-903-0387
	E-Mail Claims@NLF-INFO.com
Claims Reporting Flyer



Helpful Resources
Employer Posting Notices

	Employers are required in most states to post a Notice to Employees in a conspicuous location.  As a service to our 
	Policyholders, we provide a link from which a 
	downloadable/printable notice can be obtained for your state.

